        <name>init</name>
        <briefdescription>
<para>The init function. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<para>In case initialization still has been performed, indicated by flag init_done the function returns immediately, otherwise the PWM controller device structure will be retrieved by calling function device_get_binding. Than the function checks if the device is ready for usage with call of function device_is_ready. The return value of this function will be assigned to flag device_good. In case of an error a debug message at error level will be printed. Finally init_done flag is set to true. </para>
        </detaileddescription>
